text: Arina Rodionova and Valeriya Strakhova were the defending champions, but both players chose not to participate. Guadalupe Pérez Rojas and Daniela Seguel won the title, defeating Ágnes Bukta and Vivien Juhászová in the final, 6–7(3–7), 6–3, [11–9]. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ==References== *Main Draw Nana Trophy - Doubles
